Inputs
  • Forward - W / up arrow
  • Back - S / down arrow
  • Rotate right - D / right arrow
  • Rotate left - A / left  arrow
  • Jump - Space / num0
  • Switch  - F / Enter numpad
Share the game with your friends If you want to play with cool graphics, download the game to your computer. You can play alone or with a friend.Music
